    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape and has been well-maintained, making it a perfect match for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that still looks and feels great. It runs smoothly and the interior is super cozy. Come take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
