    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six power plant with factory individual throttle bodies. This unit exhibits a linear torque curve and crisp throttle response characteristic of its high-compression, naturally aspirated design. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise engagement, paired with a mechanical limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term structural integrity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and lateral stability synonymous with the M-chassis. A mechanically sound example optimized for the purist.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
