    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road wear consistent with careful, responsible ownership. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronic systems\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment\u2014function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It delivers a smooth, responsive ride with an engine that hums quietly and a transmission that shifts effortlessly. With a consistent service history and a smoke-free interior, this car offers a refined experience for a buyer who values longevity and class. It is ready for the road today with no immediate repairs needed.",
