    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm parting ways with my favorite ride, and honestly, she's been such a dream to own. She\u2019s been super well-loved and is still looking fantastic and running like a champ! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a fun weekend road trip, this beauty is totally ready to go and has so much life left in her. I've taken great care of her, and I'd love to see her go to a great home. Feel free to reach out if you want to take her for a spin!",
